  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "chapterTitle": "内家阐秘",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300018102_10_4569-4694",
          "range": "4569-4694",
          "rangeStart": 4569,
          "rangeEnd": 4694,
          "markText": "咏春拳的贴身近打和寸劲爆发，与通背拳的放长击远是相悖的，通背拳的招式发挥不了咏春拳的寸劲，咏春拳的短打也发挥不了通背拳的劲力优势。我想强调的是，每一门武术都有独特的劲力以及配套的技击方法。武术训练都是成体系的，光学套路根本不算学武术，初学者必须明白。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1752463109,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-07-14 11:18:29",
          "chapterUid": 10,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300018102&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=4569&rangeEnd=4694",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0dc32060813ab6d92g012a87?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=4569&rangeEnd=4694"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300018102_4_1126-1172",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1126-1172",
      "markText": "以自身的认知水平去评价天地之间所有的事情要不得，那是坐井观天，甚至固执己见而容不下其他说法。",
      "totalCount": 136,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300018102&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1126&rangeEnd=1172",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0dc32060813ab6d92g012a87?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1126&rangeEnd=1172"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300018102_3_561-589",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "561-589",
      "markText": "学功夫，最难的，恐怕不是下不了苦功，而是不能“感其意”。",
      "totalCount": 119,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300018102&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=561&rangeEnd=589",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0dc32060813ab6d92g012a87?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=561&rangeEnd=589"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300018102_4_2608-2658",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2608-2658",
      "markText": "物质可以直接继承，而精神内涵却不可以，它只能靠每一代人从头开始用功，老一辈人最多只是提供经验和方法。",
      "totalCount": 112,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300018102&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2608&rangeEnd=2658",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0dc32060813ab6d92g012a87?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2608&rangeEnd=2658"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300018102_4_1341-1386",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1341-1386",
      "markText": "现代搏击的训练，除了训练辅助器械有了进步，训练思维其实是一种退步，这是西方思维影响的结果。",
      "totalCount": 102,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300018102&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1341&rangeEnd=1386",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0dc32060813ab6d92g012a87?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1341&rangeEnd=1386"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300018102_5_2922-2980",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2922-2980",
      "markText": "当时的我承受的是整个学校的异样眼光，尽管顶着这样的压力，我依然我行我素。我喜欢，我就去做，不为外界所干扰，怡然自得。",
      "totalCount": 85,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300018102&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2922&rangeEnd=2980",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0dc32060813ab6d92g012a87?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2922&rangeEnd=2980"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300018102_7_821-853",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "821-853",
      "markText": "达摩西来一字无，全凭心意下功夫。若在纸上觅佛法，笔尖蘸干洞庭湖。",
      "totalCount": 68,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300018102&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=821&rangeEnd=853",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0dc32060813ab6d92g012a87?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=821&rangeEnd=853"
